---
title: Chicken Sausage & Garlic Flatbreads with Tomato, Onion & Mozzarella
description: In our humble opinion, flatbreads > pizza, any day! We know that may sound blasphemous, but stick with us. First of all, the golden, crispy crust is a veritable blank canvas. It’s not beholden to simply marinara and mozz! In fact, ours is topped with a creamy garlic sauce, savory chicken sausage, roasted tomato and onion, and melty mozz. Can your ’za do that?! Yeah, we didn’t think so.
